PHP CodeSniffer standard for joind.in

This is an override of the PSR2 code sniffer standard to remove the requirement
that each class must be in a namespace

Usage:
From the src/ directory, run:
    phpcs --standard=tools/codesniffer/JoindInPSR2 path/to/file/or/directory

e.g. to check the api-v2/views directory:
    phpcs --standard=tools/codesniffer/JoindInPSR2 src/views
